COMMENTS: The AMNH number of the holotype was cited in the original description. Paratypes in AMNH are: AMNH 144400 , 144401 , 101386–101388 ( 3 males , 1 female , 1 female ? from San Rafael del Norte )
;
AMNH 103428 (male from Jalapa )
;
AMNH 103429 (male from Rio Coco )
;
AMNH 102951–102953 ( 1 male and 2 females from Ocotal ). A female specimen from San Rafael del Norte , listed by Miller and Griscom in their type series, was apparently never cataloged at AMNH . Two specimens (a male and an unsexed specimen) from San Rafael del Norte that came to AMNH in 1932 with the Rothschild Collection were not available to Miller and Griscom in 1925 and are not paratypes
.
